1
00:01:45,110 --> 00:01:48,020
[Fangs of Fortune]

2
00:01:48,170 --> 00:01:50,990
[Episode 24]

3
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,760
Wen Zongyu, I'll kill you!

4
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:45,750
If you kill me,

5
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:46,750
you'll die too.

6
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:49,780
What do you mean?

7
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:52,950
Have you never felt

8
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:55,310
the burning pain in your chest?

9
00:03:09,930 --> 00:03:11,490
What did you do to me?

10
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,580
Whether it's used against a human or a demon,

11
00:03:16,220 --> 00:03:18,680
poison is always the most effective weapon.

12
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,740
If you want to live,

13
00:03:21,329 --> 00:03:23,160
you have to listen to me.

14
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,560
I, Li Lun,

15
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:28,990
never take orders from anyone!

16
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:30,590
Really?

17
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,680
Imperial Physician Liu has checked on him.

18
00:04:03,079 --> 00:04:06,100
He said Zhuo has serious internal injuries

19
00:04:06,230 --> 00:04:07,630
and his life is in danger.

20
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,360
He couldn't find the cause

21
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:13,230
and can only keep him alive with medication

22
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:15,000
and daily acupuncture.

23
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,540
Bingyi has many descendants,

24
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:22,450
but only a few can be acknowledged by the Cloud Light Sword.

25
00:04:22,529 --> 00:04:24,730
Those who are acknowledged by the Sword

26
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,540
will empathize with it.

27
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,350
The Cloud Light Sword

28
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:32,930
will then become his fate weapon.

29
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:36,210
Fate weapon?

30
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,470
Having a fate weapon means that

31
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:43,080
as long as the sword is intact,

32
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:44,650
its owner stays alive;

33
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,080
if the sword is destroyed,

34
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,300
its owner dies.

35
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:51,550
So,

36
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:54,050
that's the reason

37
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:56,190
why Zhuo is in a coma.

38
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,250
I lost control of my malicious energy…

39
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:09,050
and caused the Cloud Light Sword to crack.

40
00:05:11,350 --> 00:05:13,560
Otherwise, Li Lun alone…

41
00:05:16,590 --> 00:05:19,650
wasn't powerful enough to break the Cloud Light Sword.

42
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:24,720
Zhuo tried his best to save me,

43
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:26,780
but I…

44
00:05:29,550 --> 00:05:30,640
hurt him.

45
00:06:05,710 --> 00:06:07,150
If Jiu were here…

46
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,420
he'd definitely have a solution.

47
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:13,810
Yes.

48
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:17,650
Jiu is the most famous young physician in Tiandu.

49
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,910
He cured a lot of people.

50
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:24,750
Ms. Pei.

51
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,740
Do you think

52
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:28,240
Jiu will

53
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:30,830
return to the way he used to be?

54
00:06:36,010 --> 00:06:38,070
I'll definitely take him back

55
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:41,190
from Li Lun.

56
00:07:00,150 --> 00:07:00,870
Ah.

57
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:02,870
How about

58
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:05,050
we ask Mr. Lu Wu about it?

59
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:07,820
There are many rare herbs on Mount Kunlun.

60
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:08,910
Maybe

61
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:10,110
Mr. Lu Wu has a way

62
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:11,530
to cure Mr. Zhuo

63
00:07:11,710 --> 00:07:13,400
or wake Bai Jiu up.

64
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:18,120
Are you coming with me?

65
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:22,470
Yes.

66
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,060
Li Lun used his inner core

67
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,890
to live in Bai Jiu.

68
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,060
It's much more powerful

69
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:39,080
than possession by spells.

70
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,820
It's hard to get rid of him.

71
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,220
Is there

72
00:07:42,350 --> 00:07:44,020
no solution at all?

73
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,320
There is.

74
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:49,010
You need the help of Bingyi's descendants.

75
00:07:49,010 --> 00:07:50,030
They can use the Cloud Light Sword

76
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:53,360
to separate the parasitic primordial spirit from the host.

77
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:54,530
Cloud Light Sword?

78
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:56,390
Mr. Zhuo?

79
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,690
But I heard

80
00:08:00,990 --> 00:08:03,320
the Cloud Light Sword has been destroyed.

81
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:05,890
Mr. Lu Wu,

82
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:07,870
Mr. Zhuo

83
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:08,990
is in a coma now.

84
00:08:09,650 --> 00:08:10,750
Is there any way

85
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,900
to wake him up?

86
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,170
There is Gui Wood in the Wilderness.

87
00:08:14,170 --> 00:08:15,870
Eating it can restore his energy

88
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:18,480
and slow down his deterioration.

89
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:20,230
Gui Wood?

90
00:08:21,950 --> 00:08:22,650
Okay.

91
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,040
I got it.

92
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:26,380
Ms. Pei.

93
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,200
I'll send you back first.

94
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,290
I'll go with you.

95
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,360
No.

96
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,750
Gui Wood grows

97
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:34,820
in the crevices of black rocks along the seaside in the Wilderness.

98
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,370
Sea scorpions are everywhere.

99
00:08:36,370 --> 00:08:38,370
There are also red-bellied snakes.

100
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,919
Since it's so dangerous,

101
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,320
I can't let you go alone.

102
00:08:42,950 --> 00:08:44,309
You're still injured.

103
00:08:44,669 --> 00:08:45,780
Let me go.

104
00:08:45,809 --> 00:08:47,350
You're not familiar with the Wilderness,

105
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:48,640
and there are demons everywhere.

106
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,520
I'll go.

107
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:51,190
I'll bring Gui Wood back.

108
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:53,280
Mr. Zhuo

109
00:08:53,350 --> 00:08:55,280
is the person Jiu admires the most.

110
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:57,430
I must wake him up.

111
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,790
You should stay

112
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:01,170
to accompany Xiao.

113
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:03,970
