114
00:09:15,230 --> 00:09:15,930
Sir.

115
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,400
You're back.

116
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,400
How do you feel?

117
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,960
Thank you

118
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,260
for your treatment.

119
00:09:38,310 --> 00:09:39,960
I'm right as rain now.

120
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,940
Even better than I was

121
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:43,230
before I got hurt.

122
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,190
Commander,

123
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:51,190
according to the spy,

124
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:54,520
Zhuo Yichen from the Demon Hunting Bureau is sick and dying.

125
00:09:56,860 --> 00:09:59,890
Only Zhuo Yichen can kill Zhao Yuanzhou.

126
00:10:00,430 --> 00:10:02,130
He can't die!

127
00:10:09,950 --> 00:10:11,030
What's wrong?

128
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:21,440
Wen Zongyu's poison.

129
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,870
Poison?

130
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:26,330
This can wait.

131
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:30,310
The most important thing now is the Cloud Light Sword.

132
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,040
It can remove my primordial spirit

133
00:10:35,990 --> 00:10:38,000
from Bai Jiu's body.

134
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:41,780
It's the only thing

135
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:44,150
I'm afraid of now.

136
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:46,350
But the Cloud Light Sword

137
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,580
has been destroyed, hasn't it?

138
00:10:51,770 --> 00:10:54,030
If we can't repair the Cloud Light Sword,

139
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,470
Zhuo will keep deteriorating

140
