157
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:10,760
Once awakened, the Cloud Light Sword

158
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,270
can shake the sun and moon

159
00:12:12,290 --> 00:12:13,860
and make the earth tremble.

160
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,890
As long as the one using it is strong enough,

161
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,460
the Cloud Light Sword will awaken on itself.

162
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:32,930
Brother, you're so powerful but still can't wake it up.

163
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:35,830
I'm definitely hopeless.

164
00:12:47,010 --> 00:12:49,230
Yichen, have faith in yourself.

165
00:12:50,290 --> 00:12:51,640
After you grow up,

166
00:12:52,330 --> 00:12:54,790
you'll absolutely be more powerful than me.

167
00:12:58,070 --> 00:13:00,330
Then I'll try my best to catch up with you.

168
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,280
Okay.

169
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:06,920
But later,

170
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,900
I'll go out with Father

171
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:11,060
