172
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:13,520
When I come back,

173
00:13:13,540 --> 00:13:15,660
I'll teach you the technique just now,

174
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:16,510
okay?

175
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:18,750
Deal!

176
00:14:31,990 --> 00:14:33,120
Where is my brother?

177
00:14:37,770 --> 00:14:38,960
Say something.

178
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,490
Where is my brother?

179
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:33,380
Brother.

180
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:38,720
You promised to come back and teach me that sword technique.

181
