00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,400
Zhuo!

227
00:19:00,900 --> 00:19:01,890
Zhuo!

228
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,110
What's this?

229
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:05,950
It's the Bingyi Clan's secret heirloom that has been passed down through generations.

230
00:20:05,950 --> 00:20:07,350
The Fire-Colored Stone.

231
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:10,920
The kind of stone that Nuwa used

232
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:13,380
to mend the sky back then?

233
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,180
Yes.

234
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:17,430
But why is it

235
00:20:17,430 --> 00:20:19,890
in the pool of the Demon Hunting Bureau?

236
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:22,510
This mansion used to belong to the Zhuo family.

237
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:25,790
The Zhuo family has kept the Five-Colored Stone for generations.

238
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:27,580
It can mend the sky

239
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:29,830
and repair everything.

240
00:20:30,430 --> 00:20:31,710
So I guess

241
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:37,030
the Five-Colored Stone sensed the broken Cloud Light Sword

242
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:39,710
and showed up itself.

243
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:40,910
Great!

244
00:20:40,910 --> 00:20:41,470
But…

245
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,640
I found a way to save Zhuo.

246
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,330
Jiu?

247
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:26,230
Li Lun.

248
00:21:27,990 --> 00:21:30,250
Do you have to destroy every hope we have?

249
00:21:30,790 --> 00:21:32,700
Can't you spare Zhuo's life?

250
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:34,330
What about me?

251
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:39,170
Who will spare my life?

252
00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:43,160
Both Zhuo Yichen and Bai Jiu are my friends.

253
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:47,290
I must save them.

254
00:21:49,050 --> 00:21:51,580
