257
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:00,280
You didn't want to,

258
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:04,520
but you still did it.

259
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:07,180
You started all this.

260
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,990
You took over Jiu's body

261
00:22:10,050 --> 00:22:11,680
and live in it.

262
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:15,340
