263
00:22:16,450 --> 00:22:17,240
Oh?

264
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,600
Really?

265
00:22:24,330 --> 00:22:26,460
Then I'll wait for you to come after me.

266
00:23:00,430 --> 00:23:01,970
Fortunately, the Five-Colored Stone

267
00:23:01,970 --> 00:23:03,630
wasn't taken away by Li Lun.

268
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:25,700
It's Li Lun's vine.

269
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:33,220
The Stone has been corroded by the demonic energy of Li Lun's vine.

270
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:02,750
Zhuo!

271
00:24:06,350 --> 00:24:07,270
Zhuo!

272
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:17,590
For the greater good,

273
00:24:17,850 --> 00:24:19,620
I don't mind dying.

274
00:24:19,910 --> 00:24:20,870
Ying Long,

275
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:22,650
you don't mind dying,

276
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:25,660
but have you ever thought about my feelings?

277
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:29,310
Bingyi?

278
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:51,730
Bingyi.

279
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,070
I see.

280
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:07,310
Li Lun didn't come for the Five-Colored Stone.

281
00:25:07,550 --> 00:25:08,810
Then what does he want?

282
00:25:11,100 --> 00:25:12,640
He wants to turn Zhuo

283
00:25:15,870 --> 00:25:17,000
into a demon.

284
00:25:25,010 --> 00:25:25,870
Gui Wood!

285
00:25:25,900 --> 00:25:27,430
I've brought Gui Wood back.

286
00:25:37,770 --> 00:25:38,630
Mr. Zhuo.

287
00:25:39,410 --> 00:25:40,490
What's going on?

