573
00:42:00,590 --> 00:42:02,120
and Bai Jiu?

574
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:06,930
Jiu is the youngest among us

575
00:42:08,310 --> 00:42:10,040
and doesn't know martial arts.

576
00:42:10,750 --> 00:42:12,110
He's very timid.

577
00:42:13,330 --> 00:42:14,910
When there was danger,

578
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:18,380
he always hid behind me and Zhuo.

579
00:42:20,460 --> 00:42:22,890
I wonder how he is now.

580
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:26,580
Is he scared?

581
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,900
You treat Bai Jiu so well…

582
00:42:35,230 --> 00:42:36,870
like he's your own brother.

583
00:42:40,250 --> 00:42:42,200
I used to be weak and sick.

584
00:42:43,710 --> 00:42:45,510
You got used to taking care of me.

585
00:42:49,610 --> 00:42:51,250
Now that I'm a puppet,

586
00:42:53,310 --> 00:42:54,430
I don't feel pain

587
00:42:55,900 --> 00:42:57,150
or get hurt.

588
00:42:59,920 --> 00:43:01,770
I can protect you now.

589
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:05,630
But Bai Jiu is different.

590
00:43:07,520 --> 00:43:09,160
He really needs you.

591
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:12,210
Is that why

592
00:43:13,600 --> 00:43:15,190
you care and worry

593
00:43:16,610 --> 00:43:17,820
so much about him?

594
00:43:25,720 --> 00:43:26,520
Yes.

595
00:43:33,270 --> 00:43:34,750
But Heng

596
00:43:34,770 --> 00:43:35,810
is Heng.

597
00:43:37,230 --> 00:43:38,900
You're never anyone else,

598
00:43:40,380 --> 00:43:42,360
and you'll never be.

599
00:43:45,860 --> 00:43:47,510
No one can replace you.

600
00:43:52,280 --> 00:43:55,010
With you fighting alongside me,

601
00:43:56,950 --> 00:43:59,260
I can protect others better.

602
00:44:08,630 --> 00:44:09,750
I'm happy

603
00:44:12,050 --> 00:44:14,210
that I'm no longer your burden.

604
00:44:14,460 --> 00:44:16,900
I've become your armor.

605
00:44:18,040 --> 00:44:18,840
But...

606
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:25,090
But what?

607
00:44:31,930 --> 00:44:32,790
Nothing.

608
00:45:03,550 --> 00:45:04,190
Father.

609
00:45:04,880 --> 00:45:05,670
Cloud Light Sword.

610
00:45:05,670 --> 00:45:06,430
Zhuo.

611
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:07,400
Cloud…

612
00:45:08,470 --> 00:45:09,490
Cloud Light Sword.

613
00:45:09,490 --> 00:45:10,410
Zhuo.

614
00:45:27,330 --> 00:45:28,460
Zhuo.

615
00:45:29,850 --> 00:45:31,110
Where are you going?

616
00:45:31,280 --> 00:45:32,110
Zhuo!

